---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="mt-auto border-t border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 dark:border-slate-800 dark:bg-slate-950/60">
  <div class="container-prose grid gap-8 py-12 md:grid-cols-4">
    <div class="md:col-span-2">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-base font-bold text-brand-800 dark:text-brand-300">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" class="h-7 w-7" aria-hidden="true">
          <rect width="32" height="32" rx="7" class="fill-brand-700 dark:fill-brand-500"/>
          <circle cx="16" cy="16" r="9" stroke="white" stroke-opacity="0.6" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/>
          <ellipse cx="16" cy="16" rx="9" ry="3.6" stroke="white" stroke-opacity="0.5" stroke-width="1.2" fill="none"/>
          <ellipse cx="16" cy="16" rx="3.6" ry="9" stroke="white" stroke-opacity="0.5" stroke-width="1.2" fill="none"/>
          <circle cx="16" cy="16" r="2.4" fill="white" fill-opacity="0.85"/>
        </svg>
        quantum_proof
      </div>
      <p class="mt-3 max-w-md text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
        Open-source reversible Shor's circuits over the Oath curve family — with measured
        resource counts, ZK-proven execution traces, and a NISQ-validated proof of concept.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-500">
        Independent educational resource. Not affiliated with or endorsed by Google Quantum AI.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h4 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Project</h4>
      <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm">
        <li><a class="text-slate-700 hover:text-brand-700 dark:text-slate-300 dark:hover:text-brand-300" href="/threat">The Threat</a></li>
        <li><a class="text-slate-700 hover:text-brand-700 dark:text-slate-300 dark:hover:text-brand-300" href="/oathbreaker">Oathbreaker</a></li>
        <li><a class="text-slate-700 hover:text-brand-700 dark:text-slate-300 dark:hover:text-brand-300" href="/results">Results</a></li>
        <li><a class="text-slate-700 hover:text-brand-700 dark:text-slate-300 dark:hover:text-brand-300" href="/zkp">ZK Proof</a></li>
        <li><a class="text-slate-700 hover:text-brand-700 dark:text-slate-300 dark:hover:text-brand-300" href="/nisq">NISQ Roadmap</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h4 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Resources</h4>
      <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm">
        <li><a class="text-slate-700 hover:text-brand-700 dark:text-slate-300 dark:hover:text-brand-300" href="/docs">Documentation</a></li>
        <li><a class="text-slate-700 hover:text-brand-700 dark:text-slate-300 dark:hover:text-brand-300" href="/notebook">Notebook walkthrough</a></li>
        <li><a class="text-slate-700 hover:text-brand-700 dark:text-slate-300 dark:hover:text-brand-300" href="/ci">CI artifacts</a></li>
        <li>
          <a
            class="text-slate-700 hover:text-brand-700 dark:text-slate-300 dark:hover:text-brand-300"
            href="https://github.com/chippr-robotics/quantum_proof"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
          >GitHub</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a
            class="text-slate-700 hover:text-brand-700 dark:text-slate-300 dark:hover:text-brand-300"
            href="https://quantumai.google/static/site-assets/downloads/cryptocurrency-whitepaper.pdf"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
          >Original Google paper</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="border-t border-slate-200 py-4 text-center text-xs text-slate-500 dark:border-slate-800 dark:text-slate-500">
    © {year} chippr-robotics · MIT licensed. Built with Astro + Tailwind.
  </div>
</footer>
